
Path Optimizer using Dijkstra Algorithm

A web-based path optimization system that calculates the shortest route between two nodes using Dijkstra's Algorithm.

Features
Shortest Path Calculation
Distance Optimization
React Frontend
Flask Backend
Real-Time Route Visualization
Input Validation
Error Handling
Tech Stack
React.js
Flask
Python
JavaScript
CSS
How to Run
Frontend
npm install
npm start
Backend
pip install flask flask-cors
python server.py
Project Output
Displays the shortest path between selected nodes
Calculates total route distance
Provides a clean and responsive user interface
